-> Serverless 
Is a cloud computing model where you write and deploy code without managing servers manually.
How it works

Instead of:
        creating servers
        managing scaling
        patching OS
        handling infrastructure

You only:
        write business logic
        deploy code
        cloud provider handles the rest

Example :
        AWS Lambda
        Azure Functions
        Google Cloud Functions
